dct_description_sm: Shipping list no.: 2009-0018-S. "803361AI (G01662) 10-08." Relief shown by shading and gradient tints. Depths shown by shading and gradient tints. North Pole at map center; Greenwich meridian to the south. Includes notes in map area, texts titled "Established maritime boundaries in the Arctic region", and extensive statistical tables in right-hand margin. Shows territorial seas, continental shelf boundaries, territorial claims, shipping routes, and areas covered by sea ice. Shows Northeast Passage, Northwest Passage, Northern Sea Route.
